The Joost van der Westhuizen memorial will be broadcast live on SuperSport 1 from 12pm on Friday. It will also be streamed on supersport.com There will be a buildup from Loftus Versfeld in Pretoria from noon, with official proceedings scheduled to begin at 12.30pm. The memorial will follow the earlier church service, which will not be televised. The broadcast will conclude at 3.30pm. African News Agency